'''Bill''' is a co-worker and friend of [[Bob Yates]].

==History==
Bill came in with [[Bob Yates]] when he collapsed during a school play. He and the kids waited in the waiting room and were upset to learn that Bob had died, not knowing that he was a child molester.

==Career==
He is a teacher.
